				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$f$$\end{document} is longer than the trap release time. Due to the dominant impact of flicker noise at low frequencies, such measurements typically require long integration times (here more than 30 s for each intensity point at low intensities).

